transcript:

Customer: Manoj ji aap kya kar rahe ho sir, samajh mein nahi aa raha. Subah se try kar raha hun.
Customer: Mere liye important hai sir na sir.
Customer: Aap jo hai bina bataye call disconnect kar de rahe ho sari cheezein. Aap dekho mail open karo aap. Join kijiye aap.
Customer: Okay sir, main...
Customer: Mail aaya hua hai dekhiye aapko.
Customer: [unintelligible]
Customer: Awaaz aa rahi hai, unmute kijiye apne aapko. [unintelligible] [unintelligible] [unintelligible] [unintelligible].
